{
  "stem": "232.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And we don't look like French peasants there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "So-- and it was more-- later on, it was much, much, more obvious that I walked with my dad.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "It was about five kilometers, was a station before Luchon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "So I went out with my father, and my mother-- and sister and mother continued with the train to the end.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "Now, my dad and I was walking on a highway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "It was the route nationale in France, going into Luchon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And we were both walking, and we didn't look like peasants.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "My father with a suitcase, and I have a little bundle under my hand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And two gendarmes on bicycles passed us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "Usually, you saw a gendarme, you were shivering already, because this-- they were terrible.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "The gendarmerie in France was-- I could say as, as bad as the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "They, they helped a lot to, to, to, to make the misery bigger than it was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "Anyway, we walked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "My father said later, he said they must've gotten blind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "An angel must've been with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "They drove by.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "They didn't ask us for paper, because France was known-- when you see somebody in the street-- the authority-- let me see your papers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "Etranger means refugee.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "They take you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "It doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We made it to the village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where do we go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To the apartment where we lived before, to this printer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This printer saw us, he cried, he was so happy to see us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We explained what happened, that we come from a camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said don't worry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My son will take you in his house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was six kilometers from there, in the village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was no Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was just-- there were maybe 400 peasants-- I mean, people-- not family-- 400 people.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
